data.description:
Welcome home to sunny and warm 873 Bears Den Road.  This beautiful ranch offers 3 nice sized bedrooms with great closets and lovely original hardwood flooring.  New sliding glass door leads to large fenced in backyard.  Hang out in the partially finished basement that has LOTS of extra storage space.
As a bonus, this home boasts a spacious sunroom off the garage for even more family fun.  Use your imagination and don't hesitate! This one is going to go fast! I am telling you the way the sun hits this house, you will definitely get your viatamin D! And in the summer with the central air, it is amazing!  1 year Seller Paid Home Warranty included!  Don't let this one slip away!
